---
/**
 * SkipToContent — Accessibility skip link.
 * Visually hidden until focused, then appears at top of page.
 */
---

<a
  href="#main-content"
  class="fixed top-0 left-0 z-50 -translate-y-full bg-brand-500 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white transition-transform duration-200 focus:translate-y-0"
>
  Skip to main content
</a>
